claim: Roland Garros Stadium was constructed and remained in Paris.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Stade Roland Garros  (  `` Roland Garros Stadium '' , -LSB- stad ʁolɑ̃ ɡaʁɔs -RSB-  )  is a tennis venue located in Paris , France , that hosts the French Open -- also known as Roland Garros , particularly within Europe -- a Grand Slam championship tournament played annually around the end of May and the beginning of June .
